Son N. Nguyen completed his Ph.D. from [https://www.uta.edu/ The University of Texas at Arlington]. 
He graduated from B.E. program in December 2012 at [http://hcm.ptit.edu.vn/ Post and Telecommunications Institute of Technology].
During his Ph.D., he was a member of the [http://www.uta.edu/faculty/manry/index.html Image Processing and Neural Networks lab] at [https://www.uta.edu/uta/ The University of Texas at Arlington], under the supervision of Prof. [https://mentis.uta.edu/explore/profile/michael-manry Michael T Manry]. 
His major research areas include neural network training algorithms design, computer vision, deep learning and medical images. 


